{"tid":2490594,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人男朋友成日對自己好差","createTime":"2021-04-15T16:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T04:42:25.000Z","uid":317904,"like":4,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0de6f800404a45810d3b184304585f57f97c7d","tid":2490594,"uid":317904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"成日會將啲脾氣發落自己到 又勁易發忟憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時同佢打機 玩得差少少又比佢屌 隊友玩得差又將啲脾氣發落我到仲會鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同佢出街拍拖又成日用電話 明明之前我男朋友話我<br />\n唔好拍拖嘅時候都成日用電話 我就乖乖地聽佢話 而佢就不停用 除左食嘢嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n佢同朋友出街就成日唔覆機 有時電話都唔聽 但我同朋友出街嘅時候冇覆msg或者冇聽一個電話又會發我脾氣<br />\n<br />\n有時真係好想同佢講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我可以點做"},{"pid":"1200d264f99949496486eb0e8107f15521fe8104","tid":2490594,"uid":232466,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:50:10.000Z","msg":"錦建芬"},{"pid":"313544134d55b5467a0811d0324893cf8c7af0d5","tid":2490594,"uid":396997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:50:15.000Z","msg":"講分手"},{"pid":"7ab27bf6680cfd6127da35b8da488db73c0e40d1","tid":2490594,"uid":38904,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:50:32.000Z","msg":"咁唔成熟嘅小朋友應該要分手"},{"pid":"c0ad244adb13f4bf321b1b75f4e1f609bd9eebe6","tid":2490594,"uid":199547,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:50:42.000Z","msg":"又一pair準備分手 開心"},{"pid":"6734e7340af050cf3f2ed7fc236a4941b99a6efe","tid":2490594,"uid":168366,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:50:46.000Z","msg":"咪就係分手囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過你開得post即係唔忍心 既然係咁就繼續忍 咪放佢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a1f1809b